metadata.name: Vision #1
metadata.description: Through my mind I've traveled into the future dystopian world and was amazed by the advanced technology and towering skyscrapers that filled the city. I marveled at the sleek, high-speed transportation systems and the incredible feats of engineering that were on display everywhere I looked. However, as I explored this futuristic world, I also began to notice the dark side of this technological utopia. I saw the widespread chaos and messy system, the oppressive government and the lack of individual freedom. He realized that, despite all of its advancements, this was a world on the brink of collapse.
